      "title": "New sub station between Beliatta and Vavurukannala from Sunday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Arrangements have been made to establish a new sub-station between Beliatta and Vavurukannala railway stations for the convenience of passengers on the coastal line, the Sri Lanka Railway Station Masters' Union (SLRSMU) said.",
        "They said the new sub station is to be named as \"Nakulugamuwa\" and it is to be vested with the public on Sunday (4).",
        "The train leaving from Beliatta to Colombo Fort will stop at the new railway station on the first day, the union said. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
